.IX Item "SHRotateCoef -"
Determine the spherical harmonic coefficients of a complex function rotated by three Euler angles.
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.IX Header "SYNOPSIS"
.IP "\s-1SUBROUTINE\s0 SHRotateCoef (" 26
.IX Item "SUBROUTINE SHRotateCoef ("
